casebody.data:
STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Divonte L. LEWIS, Appellant. WD 80150 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: MAY 15, 2018 Julia E Neidhardt, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Irene C Karns, Columbia, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Before Division Four: Mark D. Pfeiffer, Chief Judge, Presiding, Alok Ahuja, Judge, Anthony Rex Gabbert, Judge

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Divonte L. Lewis appeals from a judgment entered upon a jury verdict finding him guilty of second degree murder pursuant to Section 565.021, RSMo. Cum. Supp. 2014, and armed criminal action pursuant to Section 571.015, RSMo. 2000. We affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
